Camel for sale!

26
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,510
Camel for sale!

27
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:46,760
Mister.

28
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:48,870
How about I give you my daughter,

29
00:01:49,070 --> 00:01:49,950
and you give me that camel?

30
00:01:50,070 --> 00:01:50,950
Can we exchange?

31
